replies.txt_content:
需要修改文件 , .mincraft/Flan 文件夹内

以论坛内发布的 Warage 包为例:
\.minecraft\Flan\Warage\guns\
内有 "枪械名称.txt" 如 "AG12.txt" 打开

//---Standard Gun Config for Flans Mod------------
//Created by Minecraft-SMP Toolbox 2.2.2.2


//---Standard-------------------------------------
// Naming
Name AG12
ShortName AG12


// Visuals
Model WARAGE.AG12
ModelScale 0.6
Colour 255 255 255
Icon AG12


// Recipe


//Misc

//------------------------------------------------

//---Gun------------------------------------------
//Gun Type
Deployable False


//Visual
Model WARAGE.AG12
ModelScale 0.6
Texture AG12
DeployedModel None

//Damage
Damage 14


//Ammo
Ammo AG12Ammo
BulletSpeed 30.0


//Attachments
AllowAllAttachments False
AllowAttachments aco flanMWACOG flanMW4xScope flanMWFlashlight flanMWForegrip flanMWRedDot flanMWSilencer dwLpmAimpointSight  dwLpmAssaultLight dwLpmHoloSight dwLpmAssaultGrip dwLpmRedDotSight dwSmcSharedSuppressor
AllowBarrelAttachments True
AllowScopeAttachments True
AllowStockAttachments False
AllowGripAttachments True
NumGenericAttachmentSlots 1


//Weapon Settings
Accuracy 4
Mode FullAuto
Recoil 4
ReloadTime 40
ShootDelay 2


//Shield


//Zoom
Scope None
ZoomLevel 1.0
FOVZoomLevel 1.25


//Melee


//Deployable Settings


//Sound
ShootSound AG12
ReloadSound MAReload

//------------------------------------------------



查看上方隐藏内容 即是枪支配置文件 Damage 14 即这把枪的伤害为14 , 可以按需要修改.

弹药数量修改:
\.minecraft\Flan\Warage\bullets
"AG12Ammo.txt" 打开
Name AG12Ammo
ShortName AG12Ammo
Model Bullet
//Colour of icon and model
Colour 255 255 255
Icon AG12Ammo
//How affected by gravity the bullet is
FallSpeed 0.25
//The maximum stack size
MaxStackSize 5
//The number of rounds each item has. Limited to 32000.
RoundsPerItem 35
//The damage multiplier caused by the bullet on hitting an entity
Damage 1
//Size of explosion caused
Explosion 0
//True if bullet explodes on hitting anything. Fuse denotes the maximum time it may spend in the air before detonating
ExplodeOnImpact False
Fuse 0
FlakParticles 0
//Amount of fire to spread on exploding; for each increment, it will increase the dimensions of the burning area by 2. i.e. 1 will burn a 3x3 square, 2 will burn a 5x5 square
Fire 0
BreaksGlass True
//Size of box to check for entities to hit / detonate
HitBoxSize 0.2
HitSound bullet_hit


//The penetration power of this bullet. Anything > 1 will penetrate a player. 5 ~ Jeep, 10 ~ Light Tank, 20 ~ Medium Tank, 50 = Obsidian

//Each object penetrated detracts from the bullet's power and so the total damage it does should be constant


PenetratingPower 1.0


//Particle Effects
SmokeTrail False



RoundsPerItem 35 即一个弹夹35发子弹 , 可根据需要自行修改 , 上限32000

注: flan扩展包有多种格式 (文件夹/zip/jar) 修改方式相同 本答案以 Warage 包为例 .
